# AggregatorCP SQL migration execution order (strict)
1|upgrades/001_core_telemetry_and_advice.sql|Core telemetry/event typing/advice/admin flags schema
2|upgrades/002_market_chat_and_admin_console.sql|Market/chat telemetry + admin console tables + market insights
3|upgrades/003_housekeeping_and_index_hardening.sql|Housekeeping metrics + late index hardening and uniqueness constraints
4|upgrades/004_acp_admin_console_tables.sql|AggregatorCP admin/action/bridge queue tables with acp_ prefix
5|upgrades/005_acp_watch_cases.sql|Watch Center cases/events for scheduled monitoring and webhook alerts
6|upgrades/006_acp_watch_case_rules_and_stats.sql|Watch Center criteria rules, thresholds and checks counter
